# Test fixtures are compared byte-for-byte against their compressed twins,
# which are binary blobs holding LF line endings. Force LF on the plain text
# fixtures on every platform so a Windows checkout (autocrlf) does not rewrite
# them to CRLF and break the comparison; keep the compressed fixtures binary so
# they are never touched.
*.xyz text eol=lf
*.extxyz text eol=lf
*.gz binary
*.zst binary
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
